import React from 'react'
import {
       SidebarContainer,
       Icon,
       CloseIcon,
       SideBtnWrap,
       SidebarMenu,
       SidebarRoute,
       SidebarWrapper
       

} from './SidebarElements'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
           <Icon>
              <CloseIcon/>
           </Icon>
           <SidebarWrapper>
               <SidebarMenu>
                   <SidebarLink to="about">
                       About
                   </SidebarLink>
                   <SidebarLink to="discover">
                       Discover
                   </SidebarLink>
                   <SidebarLink to="services">
                       Services
                   </SidebarLink>
                   <SidebarLink to="signup ">
                       Sign Up
                   </SidebarLink>
               </SidebarMenu>

               <SideBtnWrap>
                   <SidebarRoute to="/signin">Sign In</SidebarRoute>
               </SideBtnWrap>
           </SidebarWrapper>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
